- I can't see them.

01:34.594 --> 01:36.595
Shit, he's bleeding a lot.

01:36.721 --> 01:39.264
- Stop the bleeding.
- I can't.

01:39.390 --> 01:41.683
- Use your finger.
- There's too much.

01:43.394 --> 01:45.854
Here come those bastards. Faster!

01:45.980 --> 01:47.815
Fuck!

01:47.941 --> 01:49.066
Faster!

01:51.444 --> 01:53.028
Motherfuckers!

01:58.243 --> 02:00.160
- Fucking hell!
- Watch out!

02:10.380 --> 02:12.089
- Shit, he fell.
- Is he dead?

02:12.215 --> 02:15.509
Why did you fuck
with those bastards?

02:15.635 --> 02:17.678
Is he dead?

02:17.804 --> 02:19.054
Answer me!

02:19.180 --> 02:23.684
No, but he keeps falling.
He's bleeding even more!

02:27.605 --> 02:28.981
I've covered his wound.

02:29.107 --> 02:30.941
Get down!

02:32.026 --> 02:34.319
They've got a fucking gun!

02:50.086 --> 02:53.255
Hurry! Let's go to Chilaquil's.

02:57.468 --> 02:58.927
Motherfucker!

03:01.681 --> 03:04.099
- Faster.
- Get down, man.

03:09.314 --> 03:11.148
Step on it!

03:23.912 --> 03:27.748
The window! The window, that's it!

03:29.918 --> 03:35.714
Octavio and Susana

03:55.652 --> 03:57.277
Are you ready?

03:58.780 --> 04:00.155
What's your stake?

04:01.115 --> 04:02.407
Ten thousand.

04:03.534 --> 04:05.535
OK for 10,000?

04:06.412 --> 04:07.621
Go on then.

04:09.082 --> 04:10.832
You're on for 10.

04:10.959 --> 04:13.585
10's the stake.

04:24.681 --> 04:26.431
Heat 'em up!

04:35.608 --> 04:37.067
Marks!

04:41.155 --> 04:42.864
Let them go!

04:56.045 --> 04:57.421
Cofi!

04:58.506 --> 04:59.965
Cofi, come here!

05:04.387 --> 05:06.388
Fucking dog!

05:20.570 --> 05:22.612
