05:59.067 --> 06:00.859
I raised my children,

06:01.611 --> 06:03.695
now you raise yours.

06:36.687 --> 06:38.355
Go on, Turco!

06:41.943 --> 06:43.860
Get him, eat him!

06:43.986 --> 06:46.071
