I was dying, I was as dead
as I could be.

2:27:27.421 --> 2:27:29.339
I'll be back to find you...

2:27:30.925 --> 2:27:33.885
once I have the courage
to look you in the eyes.

2:27:35.137 --> 2:27:38.223
I love you, my little girl.

2:28:15.595 --> 2:28:17.345
What's your dog called?

2:28:20.349 --> 2:28:22.267
Blackie.

2:28:24.228 --> 2:28:25.854
Shut up, Blackie!

2:28:25.980 --> 2:28:28.023
- See you around.
- Bye.

2:29:27.333 --> 2:29:31.670
For Luciano, because we are also
what we have lost.
